Package: matclust
Type: Package
Title: Clustering for matrix-variate normal data with uneven replecations
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-04-20
Description: Finite mixture model for replicated data without discarding
    replicate information. There may be an unequal number of replicates between
    features of each observation, allowing for "jagged" observations.
